law.catch_line: Surrender and forwarding of suspended or revoked licenses.
law.text: All licenses suspended or revoked pursuant to KRS 189A.010(6), 189A.070, 189A.107, 189A.200, or 189A.220 shall be surrendered to the court and forwarded to the Transportation Cabinet.
law.history: Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 467, sec. 6, effective October 1, 2000. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 165, sec. 8, effective July 13, 1984.
